                        e.getMessage());
            }
        }

        // Legacy key=value format (only for simple values without commas/colons)
        Map<String, String> map = new LinkedHashMap<>();
        for (String pair : trimmed.split(",")) {
            String[] kv = pair.split("=", 2);
            if (kv.length == 2) {
